original_sql: SELECT MIN(c.c_name) AS min_c_c_name, COUNT(c.c_address) AS count_c_c_address, SUM(c.c_custkey) AS sum_c_c_custkey, c.c_address AS c_c_address, COUNT(o.o_comment) AS count_o_o_comment FROM customer c, orders o WHERE c.c_custkey = (SELECT COUNT(DISTINCT l_shipmode) FROM lineitem JOIN (SELECT o_orderkey FROM orders UNION ALL SELECT o_orderkey FROM orders WHERE o_shippriority = 1) AS order_union_1 ON lineitem.l_orderkey = order_union_1.o_orderkey) AND o.o_orderkey IN (SELECT DISTINCT o_orderkey FROM orders UNION SELECT l_orderkey FROM lineitem WHERE l_quantity > 30) AND EXISTS (SELECT DISTINCT p_retailprice FROM (SELECT p_retailprice FROM part UNION ALL SELECT c_acctbal FROM customer) AS u_3 JOIN lineitem ON u_3.p_retailprice = l_tax) AND c.c_acctbal > (SELECT COUNT(DISTINCT s_suppkey) FROM supplier WHERE s_nationkey IN (SELECT n_nationkey FROM nation WHERE n_regionkey = 3) AND s_acctbal < 3000 AND s_phone LIKE '27%') AND EXISTS (SELECT c_address FROM (SELECT c_address, c_mktsegment FROM customer WHERE c_mktsegment = 'AUTOMOBILE' ) AS subq_5 WHERE c_mktsegment != 'BUILDING' ORDER BY c_mktsegment) AND o.o_custkey = c.c_custkey AND o.o_orderdate <= '1992-07-08' AND o.o_orderpriority LIKE '4-NOT SPECIFIED%' AND c.c_nationkey > 12 AND c.c_custkey >= 19833 AND o.o_custkey = 104377  GROUP BY c.c_address LIMIT 100;

SELECT MAX(s.s_nationkey) AS max_s_s_nationkey, MAX(p.p_comment) AS max_p_p_comment, COUNT(s.s_suppkey) AS count_s_s_suppkey, COUNT(p.p_mfgr) AS count_p_p_mfgr, COUNT(p.p_brand) AS count_p_p_brand FROM part p, supplier s WHERE EXISTS (SELECT c_comment FROM (SELECT c_comment, c_custkey FROM customer ) AS subq_1 UNION SELECT l_shipmode FROM lineitem) AND EXISTS (SELECT COUNT(DISTINCT o_orderkey) FROM orders WHERE o_orderpriority = '1-URGENT' UNION SELECT COUNT(DISTINCT ps_partkey) FROM partsupp WHERE ps_supplycost > 100) AND s.s_address IN (SELECT DISTINCT s_address FROM supplier UNION SELECT s_phone FROM supplier WHERE s_nationkey = 10) AND p.p_brand IN (SELECT p_brand FROM (SELECT p_brand, p_retailprice FROM part ) AS subq_4 UNION SELECT s_comment FROM supplier) AND p.p_size > (SELECT COUNT(*) FROM (SELECT o_totalprice FROM orders UNION ALL SELECT l_extendedprice FROM lineitem ) t) AND s.s_suppkey >= 1356 AND p.p_container LIKE 'MED BAG%' AND p.p_retailprice >= 1135.6874317944726 AND p.p_size >= 10 AND p.p_brand LIKE 'Brand#41%'  LIMIT 50;

SELECT SUM(l.l_orderkey) AS sum_l_l_orderkey, COUNT(l.l_shipinstruct) AS count_l_l_shipinstruct, COUNT(l.l_suppkey) AS count_l_l_suppkey, MAX(l.l_tax) AS max_l_l_tax, MIN(l.l_returnflag) AS min_l_l_returnflag FROM customer c, lineitem l, partsupp ps WHERE c.c_acctbal = (SELECT COUNT(*) FROM (SELECT o_clerk FROM orders UNION ALL SELECT p_mfgr FROM part ) t) AND l.l_tax = (SELECT COUNT(DISTINCT l_linenumber) FROM (SELECT l_linenumber, l_discount FROM lineitem WHERE l_extendedprice > 1000 ) t) AND EXISTS (SELECT MAX(p_retailprice) FROM (SELECT p_retailprice, p_container FROM part WHERE p_size > 10 UNION ALL SELECT p_retailprice, p_container FROM part WHERE p_size <= 10 GROUP BY p_retailprice, p_container) p JOIN (SELECT ps_partkey, ps_supplycost FROM partsupp) ps ON p.p_retailprice = ps.ps_partkey GROUP BY ps.ps_supplycost) AND l.l_extendedprice = (SELECT COUNT(DISTINCT p_partkey) FROM (SELECT p_partkey, p_name FROM part WHERE p_size > 20 ) t) AND ps.ps_supplycost > (SELECT COUNT(DISTINCT l_orderkey) FROM (SELECT l_orderkey FROM lineitem WHERE l_shipdate > '1998-01-01' UNION ALL SELECT o_orderkey FROM orders WHERE o_orderdate < '1995-01-01') t JOIN customer ON c_custkey = t.l_orderkey) AND ps.ps_partkey = l.l_partkey AND ps.ps_suppkey = l.l_suppkey AND ps.ps_supplycost = 640.9723574611052 AND c.c_custkey <= 19213 AND l.l_shipmode LIKE 'MAIL%' AND ps.ps_suppkey = 2268 AND c.c_name LIKE 'Customer#000010237%'  LIMIT 50;

SELECT SUM(l.l_tax) AS sum_l_l_tax, s.s_phone AS s_s_phone, MAX(s.s_acctbal) AS max_s_s_acctbal, COUNT(l.l_quantity) AS count_l_l_quantity, AVG(l.l_quantity) AS avg_l_l_quantity FROM lineitem l, partsupp ps, supplier s WHERE ps.ps_supplycost = (SELECT COUNT(*) FROM (SELECT o_orderpriority FROM orders UNION ALL SELECT p_container FROM part ) t) AND l.l_quantity > (SELECT COUNT(DISTINCT r_regionkey) FROM region WHERE r_name = 'ASIA' AND (r_regionkey = 1 OR r_regionkey = 2) AND r_comment LIKE 'B%') AND s.s_suppkey = (SELECT COUNT(DISTINCT p_size) FROM part JOIN (SELECT ps_partkey FROM partsupp UNION ALL SELECT ps_partkey FROM partsupp WHERE ps_supplycost < 10) AS partsupp_union_3 ON part.p_partkey = partsupp_union_3.ps_partkey) AND EXISTS (SELECT DISTINCT p_comment FROM part UNION SELECT DISTINCT s_comment FROM supplier WHERE s_acctbal < 3500 UNION SELECT DISTINCT l_comment FROM lineitem WHERE l_quantity > 20) AND EXISTS (SELECT n_5.n_name FROM nation n_5 WHERE n_5.n_nationkey IN (SELECT c_5.c_nationkey FROM customer c_5 WHERE c_5.c_acctbal > 500 UNION ALL SELECT s_5.s_nationkey FROM supplier s_5 WHERE s_5.s_acctbal < 1000 GROUP BY s_5.s_nationkey) AND n_5.n_regionkey = 2) AND ps.ps_suppkey = s.s_suppkey AND ps.ps_partkey = l.l_partkey AND ps.ps_suppkey = l.l_suppkey AND l.l_orderkey <= 3036724 AND l.l_partkey > 69675 AND l.l_commitdate < '1997-11-23' AND s.s_acctbal > 2692.4439012736166 AND l.l_suppkey = 9700  GROUP BY s.s_phone LIMIT 100;

SELECT COUNT(c.c_mktsegment) AS count_c_c_mktsegment, MIN(l.l_commitDATE) AS min_l_l_commitDATE, AVG(c.c_acctbal) AS avg_c_c_acctbal, l.l_suppkey AS l_l_suppkey, c.c_name AS c_c_name FROM customer c, lineitem l, nation n WHERE EXISTS (SELECT l_shipmode FROM (SELECT l_shipmode, l_quantity FROM lineitem ) AS subq_1 UNION SELECT c_phone FROM customer) AND n.n_nationkey > (SELECT COUNT(DISTINCT c_custkey) FROM (SELECT c_custkey FROM customer WHERE c_acctbal > 5000 UNION ALL SELECT o_custkey FROM orders WHERE o_totalprice < 1000) t JOIN nation ON n_nationkey = t.c_custkey) AND c.c_phone IN (SELECT c_phone FROM (SELECT c_phone, c_mktsegment FROM customer ) AS subq_3 UNION SELECT p_type FROM part) AND c.c_address IN (SELECT c_address FROM customer WHERE c_custkey IN (SELECT o_custkey FROM orders WHERE o_orderdate < '1995-01-01' UNION SELECT o_custkey FROM orders WHERE o_orderpriority = '2-HIGH')) AND l.l_quantity = (SELECT COUNT(DISTINCT o_custkey) FROM (SELECT o_custkey, o_totalprice FROM orders WHERE o_totalprice > 50000 ) t) AND n.n_nationkey = c.c_nationkey AND l.l_discount > 0.08186304619445509 AND l.l_tax <= 0.05622575236281226 AND c.c_mktsegment LIKE 'HOUSEHOLD%' AND n.n_regionkey = 0 AND l.l_linestatus LIKE 'O%'  GROUP BY c.c_name, l.l_suppkey LIMIT 50;

SELECT l.l_extendedprice AS l_l_extendedprice, COUNT(p.p_mfgr) AS count_p_p_mfgr, MIN(p.p_container) AS min_p_p_container, MIN(p.p_retailprice) AS min_p_p_retailprice, COUNT(l.l_quantity) AS count_l_l_quantity FROM customer c, lineitem l, nation n, part p WHERE l.l_extendedprice > (SELECT COUNT(*) FROM (SELECT p_brand FROM part UNION ALL SELECT n_name FROM nation ) t) AND c.c_custkey = (SELECT COUNT(DISTINCT ps_partkey) FROM (SELECT ps_partkey, ps_supplycost FROM partsupp WHERE ps_availqty > 50 ) t) AND p.p_retailprice = (SELECT COUNT(DISTINCT r_regionkey) FROM region WHERE r_name = 'EUROPE' AND (r_regionkey = 1 OR r_regionkey = 2) AND 9+9=18 AND r_regionkey IN (SELECT n_regionkey FROM nation WHERE n_name = 'GERMANY' AND 10*11=110)) AND n.n_regionkey = (SELECT COUNT(DISTINCT p_partkey) FROM part WHERE p_size IN (SELECT ps_partkey FROM partsupp WHERE ps_supplycost < 10 UNION SELECT ps_partkey FROM partsupp WHERE ps_availqty > 100)) AND l.l_extendedprice > (SELECT COUNT(DISTINCT o_orderkey) FROM orders WHERE o_custkey IN (SELECT c_custkey FROM customer WHERE c_acctbal < 500 INTERSECT SELECT c_custkey FROM customer WHERE c_mktsegment = 'BUILDING')) AND n.n_nationkey = c.c_nationkey AND c.c_nationkey >= 22 AND n.n_name LIKE 'IRAN%' AND p.p_mfgr LIKE 'Manufacturer#1%' AND p.p_name LIKE 'bisque antique orange misty pale%' AND p.p_brand LIKE 'Brand#22%'  GROUP BY l.l_extendedprice LIMIT 100;

SELECT o.o_comment AS o_o_comment, MIN(ps.ps_suppkey) AS min_ps_ps_suppkey, MAX(ps.ps_supplycost) AS max_ps_ps_supplycost, COUNT(ps.ps_comment) AS count_ps_ps_comment, SUM(c.c_acctbal) AS sum_c_c_acctbal FROM customer c, orders o, partsupp ps WHERE o.o_orderstatus IN (SELECT o_orderstatus FROM (SELECT o_orderstatus, o_totalprice FROM orders WHERE o_totalprice = 5000 ) AS subq_1 WHERE o_totalprice > 3000 ORDER BY o_totalprice) AND EXISTS (SELECT COUNT(*) FROM (SELECT c_mktsegment FROM customer UNION SELECT p_type FROM (SELECT p_type, COUNT(*) FROM part GROUP BY p_type HAVING COUNT(*) > 4) AS subq_2) AS t_2) AND c.c_nationkey = (SELECT COUNT(DISTINCT s_suppkey) FROM supplier WHERE s_nationkey IN (SELECT n_nationkey FROM nation WHERE n_regionkey = 1) AND s_acctbal > 4000 AND s_phone LIKE '18%') AND ps.ps_availqty = (SELECT COUNT(DISTINCT o_custkey) FROM orders JOIN (SELECT c_custkey FROM customer UNION ALL SELECT c_custkey FROM customer WHERE c_acctbal > 1000) AS cust_union_4 ON orders.o_custkey = cust_union_4.c_custkey) AND c.c_phone IN (SELECT DISTINCT c_phone FROM customer UNION SELECT DISTINCT s_phone FROM supplier WHERE s_acctbal > 5000 UNION SELECT DISTINCT l_returnflag FROM lineitem WHERE l_discount < 0.05) AND o.o_custkey = c.c_custkey AND ps.ps_supplycost < 282.24919439580907 AND c.c_custkey >= 53828 AND c.c_mktsegment LIKE 'MACHINERY%' AND o.o_totalprice = 489531.45826834353 AND ps.ps_suppkey < 6721  GROUP BY o.o_comment LIMIT 30;

SELECT SUM(l.l_tax) AS sum_l_l_tax, MAX(l.l_receiptDATE) AS max_l_l_receiptDATE, AVG(s.s_acctbal) AS avg_s_s_acctbal, AVG(l.l_suppkey) AS avg_l_l_suppkey, COUNT(l.l_receiptDATE) AS count_l_l_receiptDATE FROM lineitem l, orders o, supplier s WHERE EXISTS (SELECT AVG(l_extendedprice) FROM (SELECT l_extendedprice, l_shipmode FROM lineitem JOIN supplier ON l_suppkey = s_suppkey WHERE l_tax > 0.02 ) AS t_1 GROUP BY l_shipmode ORDER BY l_shipmode) AND l.l_quantity = (SELECT COUNT(DISTINCT o_orderkey) FROM orders WHERE o_custkey IN (SELECT c_custkey FROM customer WHERE c_acctbal < 500 INTERSECT SELECT c_custkey FROM customer WHERE c_mktsegment = 'BUILDING')) AND EXISTS (SELECT AVG(l_quantity) FROM (SELECT l_quantity, l_linestatus FROM lineitem JOIN part ON l_partkey = p_partkey ) AS t_3 GROUP BY l_linestatus ORDER BY l_linestatus) AND o.o_clerk IN (SELECT o_clerk FROM (SELECT o_clerk, o_totalprice FROM orders ) AS subq_4 UNION SELECT p_name FROM part) AND s.s_nationkey > (SELECT COUNT(DISTINCT l_linenumber) FROM (SELECT l_linenumber FROM lineitem WHERE l_quantity > 20 UNION ALL SELECT o_shippriority FROM orders WHERE o_totalprice < 500) t JOIN part ON p_partkey = t.l_linenumber) AND o.o_orderkey = l.l_orderkey AND l.l_extendedprice <= 11821.277969397044 AND s.s_nationkey >= 7 AND l.l_linestatus LIKE 'O%' AND s.s_suppkey = 7743 AND l.l_quantity < 18.001401603940515  LIMIT 100;

SELECT COUNT(s.s_name) AS count_s_s_name, SUM(s.s_suppkey) AS sum_s_s_suppkey, MIN(o.o_orderDATE) AS min_o_o_orderDATE, MIN(s.s_address) AS min_s_s_address, MAX(s.s_comment) AS max_s_s_comment FROM orders o, supplier s WHERE s.s_acctbal > (SELECT (16 * 4) + COUNT(DISTINCT p_partkey) FROM part WHERE p_container IN (SELECT l_shipmode FROM lineitem WHERE l_returnflag = 'N')) AND o.o_orderkey = (SELECT COUNT(*) FROM (SELECT r_name FROM region UNION ALL SELECT n_name FROM nation ) t) AND EXISTS (SELECT o_3.o_orderstatus FROM orders o_3 WHERE o_3.o_orderkey IN (SELECT l_3.l_orderkey FROM lineitem l_3 WHERE l_3.l_quantity < 15 UNION ALL SELECT l2_3.l_orderkey FROM lineitem l2_3 WHERE l2_3.l_extendedprice > 800 GROUP BY l2_3.l_orderkey) AND o_3.o_totalprice > 3000) AND s.s_nationkey = (SELECT COUNT(DISTINCT o_orderkey) FROM orders JOIN (SELECT c_custkey FROM customer WHERE c_mktsegment = 'BUILDING' UNION ALL SELECT c_custkey FROM customer WHERE c_acctbal < 500) AS cust_union_4 ON orders.o_custkey = cust_union_4.c_custkey) AND o.o_totalprice = (SELECT COUNT(DISTINCT p_size) FROM part JOIN (SELECT ps_partkey FROM partsupp UNION ALL SELECT ps_partkey FROM partsupp WHERE ps_supplycost < 10) AS partsupp_union_5 ON part.p_partkey = partsupp_union_5.ps_partkey) AND o.o_custkey > 55669 AND s.s_nationkey < 11 AND s.s_name LIKE 'Supplier#000002383%' AND s.s_acctbal > 1133.3521214999548 AND o.o_orderstatus LIKE 'O%'  LIMIT 50;

SELECT MAX(ps.ps_supplycost) AS max_ps_ps_supplycost, MAX(c.c_comment) AS max_c_c_comment, AVG(c.c_acctbal) AS avg_c_c_acctbal, AVG(c.c_custkey) AS avg_c_c_custkey, SUM(c.c_custkey) AS sum_c_c_custkey FROM customer c, partsupp ps WHERE c.c_acctbal = (SELECT COUNT(*) FROM (SELECT o_orderstatus FROM orders UNION ALL SELECT l_returnflag FROM lineitem ) t) AND ps.ps_partkey > (SELECT COUNT(DISTINCT o_orderkey) FROM orders WHERE o_custkey IN (SELECT c_custkey FROM customer WHERE c_acctbal > 1000 UNION SELECT c_custkey FROM customer WHERE c_mktsegment = 'AUTOMOBILE')) AND c.c_acctbal = (SELECT COUNT(DISTINCT o_orderkey) FROM orders WHERE o_custkey IN (SELECT c_custkey FROM customer WHERE c_acctbal < 800 INTERSECT SELECT c_custkey FROM customer WHERE c_mktsegment = 'HOUSEHOLD')) AND c.c_custkey IN (SELECT DISTINCT c_custkey FROM customer UNION SELECT o_custkey FROM orders WHERE o_totalprice > 1000) AND EXISTS (SELECT o_5.o_orderpriority FROM orders o_5 WHERE o_5.o_orderkey IN (SELECT l_5.l_orderkey FROM lineitem l_5 WHERE l_5.l_shipmode = 'AIR' UNION ALL SELECT l2_5.l_orderkey FROM lineitem l2_5 WHERE l2_5.l_returnflag = 'N' GROUP BY l2_5.l_orderkey) AND o_5.o_totalprice > 2000) AND c.c_custkey = 79709 AND c.c_name LIKE 'Customer#000014242%' AND ps.ps_supplycost < 146.79215144466542 AND c.c_nationkey <= 0 AND ps.ps_partkey > 152741  LIMIT 50;

SELECT MAX(p.p_type) AS max_p_p_type, SUM(ps.ps_suppkey) AS sum_ps_ps_suppkey, MAX(r.r_name) AS max_r_r_name, MAX(p.p_retailprice) AS max_p_p_retailprice, COUNT(p.p_size) AS count_p_p_size FROM part p, partsupp ps, region r WHERE p.p_mfgr IN (SELECT DISTINCT p_mfgr FROM part UNION SELECT s_name FROM supplier UNION SELECT s_name FROM (SELECT DISTINCT s_name FROM supplier AS s1_1 WHERE s_acctbal < 5000) AS subq_1) AND r.r_comment IN (SELECT r_comment FROM (SELECT r_comment, r_regionkey FROM region WHERE r_regionkey = 3 ) AS subq_2 WHERE r_regionkey > 2 ORDER BY r_regionkey) AND ps.ps_availqty = (SELECT COUNT(*) FROM (SELECT c_mktsegment FROM customer UNION ALL SELECT l_shipmode FROM lineitem ) t) AND EXISTS (SELECT SUM(l_discount) FROM (SELECT l_discount, l_linestatus FROM lineitem WHERE l_shipdate BETWEEN DATE '1998-01-01' AND DATE '1998-12-31' ) t GROUP BY l_linestatus ORDER BY l_linestatus) AND EXISTS (SELECT MAX(c_acctbal) FROM (SELECT c_acctbal, c_mktsegment FROM customer WHERE c_nationkey BETWEEN 10 AND 20 ) t GROUP BY c_mktsegment ORDER BY c_mktsegment) AND ps.ps_partkey = p.p_partkey AND ps.ps_partkey <= 43960 AND p.p_container LIKE 'LG CASE%' AND p.p_mfgr LIKE 'Manufacturer#1%' AND p.p_type LIKE 'ECONOMY PLATED COPPER%' AND p.p_name LIKE 'burlywood blanched gainsboro antique peru%'  LIMIT 10;

SELECT p.p_type AS p_p_type, r.r_name AS r_r_name, COUNT(p.p_comment) AS count_p_p_comment, MAX(r.r_name) AS max_r_r_name, MIN(p.p_brand) AS min_p_p_brand FROM part p, partsupp ps, region r WHERE p.p_size > (SELECT COUNT(DISTINCT n_nationkey) FROM nation JOIN (SELECT s_nationkey FROM supplier WHERE s_acctbal < 2000 UNION ALL SELECT s_nationkey FROM supplier WHERE s_comment LIKE '%reliable%') AS subq_1 ON nation.n_nationkey = subq_1.s_nationkey) AND EXISTS (SELECT MAX(l_discount) FROM (SELECT l_discount, l_shipmode FROM lineitem WHERE l_commitdate BETWEEN DATE '1993-01-01' AND DATE '1993-12-31' ) t GROUP BY l_shipmode ORDER BY l_shipmode) AND r.r_regionkey = (SELECT COUNT(DISTINCT s_name) FROM (SELECT s_name FROM supplier WHERE s_acctbal > 8000 EXCEPT SELECT c_name FROM customer WHERE c_acctbal < 1500 ) AS subquery_3) AND EXISTS (SELECT MAX(p_retailprice) FROM (SELECT p_retailprice, p_container FROM part WHERE p_size > 10 UNION ALL SELECT p_retailprice, p_container FROM part WHERE p_size <= 10 GROUP BY p_retailprice, p_container) p JOIN (SELECT ps_partkey, ps_supplycost FROM partsupp) ps ON p.p_retailprice = ps.ps_partkey GROUP BY ps.ps_supplycost) AND ps.ps_partkey > (SELECT COUNT(DISTINCT c_custkey) FROM customer WHERE c_acctbal < 3000 AND (c_nationkey = 15 OR c_nationkey = 20) AND 5+5=10 AND c_nationkey IN (SELECT n_nationkey FROM nation WHERE n_regionkey = 2 AND 6*7=42)) AND ps.ps_partkey = p.p_partkey AND ps.ps_partkey = 184560 AND p.p_retailprice <= 1660.8268146231107 AND p.p_name LIKE 'puff metallic papaya gainsboro cornsilk%' AND ps.ps_supplycost >= 712.4638698652685 AND p.p_container LIKE 'WRAP BAG%'  GROUP BY p.p_type, r.r_name LIMIT 10;

SELECT COUNT(o.o_shippriority) AS count_o_o_shippriority, MIN(o.o_shippriority) AS min_o_o_shippriority, AVG(o.o_totalprice) AS avg_o_o_totalprice, MIN(o.o_orderDATE) AS min_o_o_orderDATE, o.o_orderkey AS o_o_orderkey FROM orders o WHERE EXISTS (SELECT COUNT(o_orderkey) FROM (SELECT o_orderkey, o_orderstatus FROM orders JOIN customer ON o_custkey = c_custkey WHERE c_mktsegment = 'BUILDING' UNION SELECT o_orderkey, o_orderstatus FROM orders JOIN lineitem ON o_orderkey = l_orderkey WHERE l_quantity > 20 AND l_shipdate IN (SELECT l_shipdate FROM lineitem WHERE l_receiptdate < '1996-01-01')) AS subq_1 GROUP BY o_orderstatus) AND o.o_clerk IN (SELECT o_clerk FROM orders WHERE o_orderkey IN (SELECT l_orderkey FROM lineitem WHERE l_extendedprice > 5000 ) UNION SELECT o_clerk FROM orders WHERE o_orderkey IN (SELECT l_orderkey FROM lineitem WHERE l_extendedprice < 5000 ) ORDER BY o_clerk) AND o.o_orderpriority IN (SELECT DISTINCT o_orderpriority FROM orders UNION SELECT DISTINCT c_mktsegment FROM customer WHERE c_acctbal < 1000 UNION SELECT DISTINCT l_shipinstruct FROM lineitem WHERE l_tax > 0.1) AND EXISTS (SELECT r_comment FROM (SELECT r_comment, r_regionkey FROM region ) AS subq_4 UNION SELECT l_comment FROM lineitem) AND EXISTS (SELECT o_clerk FROM (SELECT o_clerk FROM orders WHERE o_orderkey IN (SELECT l_orderkey FROM lineitem WHERE l_receiptdate > '1995-06-01' ) UNION ALL SELECT o_clerk FROM orders WHERE o_totalprice < 500) t GROUP BY o_clerk ORDER BY o_clerk) AND o.o_custkey >= 111045 AND o.o_totalprice >= 243212.594797091 AND o.o_orderpriority LIKE '1-URGENT%' AND o.o_orderkey >= 243983 AND o.o_orderstatus LIKE 'F%'  GROUP BY o.o_orderkey LIMIT 10;

SELECT SUM(l.l_linenumber) AS sum_l_l_linenumber, MAX(l.l_receiptDATE) AS max_l_l_receiptDATE, COUNT(l.l_linestatus) AS count_l_l_linestatus, MAX(l.l_suppkey) AS max_l_l_suppkey, MAX(l.l_extendedprice) AS max_l_l_extendedprice FROM lineitem l WHERE l.l_partkey > (SELECT COUNT(DISTINCT s_suppkey) FROM supplier WHERE s_acctbal < 1000 AND (s_nationkey = 1 OR s_nationkey = 2) AND s_phone LIKE '10%') AND EXISTS (SELECT s_name FROM (SELECT s_name FROM supplier WHERE s_suppkey IN (SELECT ps_suppkey FROM partsupp WHERE ps_supplycost > 10 ) UNION ALL SELECT s_name FROM supplier WHERE s_acctbal > 5000) t GROUP BY s_name ORDER BY s_name) AND EXISTS (SELECT o_clerk FROM orders WHERE o_custkey IN (SELECT c_custkey FROM customer WHERE c_acctbal > 2000 UNION SELECT o_custkey FROM orders WHERE o_orderdate < '1993-06-30') AND o_shippriority IN (SELECT o_shippriority FROM orders JOIN customer ON o_custkey = c_custkey WHERE c_mktsegment = 'HOUSEHOLD')) AND EXISTS (SELECT COUNT(*) FROM (SELECT c_nationkey FROM customer UNION SELECT s_nationkey FROM (SELECT s_nationkey, COUNT(*) FROM supplier GROUP BY s_nationkey HAVING COUNT(*) > 4) AS subq_4) AS t_4) AND EXISTS (SELECT DISTINCT r_name FROM region UNION SELECT p_type FROM part UNION SELECT p_type FROM (SELECT DISTINCT p_type FROM part AS p1_5 WHERE p_retailprice < 50) AS subq_5) AND l.l_shipdate > '1997-04-19' AND l.l_receiptdate >= '1993-08-07' AND l.l_discount = 0.06997157289029109 AND l.l_partkey < 88396 AND l.l_returnflag LIKE 'R%'  LIMIT 10;

SELECT MIN(l.l_comment) AS min_l_l_comment, MIN(l.l_shipmode) AS min_l_l_shipmode, MIN(s.s_address) AS min_s_s_address, COUNT(l.l_orderkey) AS count_l_l_orderkey, MAX(s.s_comment) AS max_s_s_comment FROM lineitem l, supplier s WHERE EXISTS (SELECT p_type FROM (SELECT p_type, p_partkey FROM part WHERE p_partkey = 9 ) AS subq_1 WHERE p_partkey > 8 ORDER BY p_partkey) AND EXISTS (SELECT p_mfgr FROM (SELECT p_mfgr FROM part WHERE p_partkey IN (SELECT ps_partkey FROM partsupp WHERE ps_availqty < 30 ) UNION ALL SELECT p_mfgr FROM part WHERE p_retailprice < 50) t GROUP BY p_mfgr ORDER BY p_mfgr) AND s.s_suppkey IN (SELECT DISTINCT s_suppkey FROM supplier UNION SELECT ps_suppkey FROM partsupp WHERE ps_supplycost < 50) AND l.l_orderkey = (SELECT COUNT(DISTINCT l_suppkey) FROM (SELECT l_suppkey FROM lineitem WHERE l_discount > 0.05 UNION ALL SELECT ps_suppkey FROM partsupp WHERE ps_supplycost > 60) t JOIN part ON p_partkey = t.l_suppkey) AND EXISTS (SELECT c_phone FROM (SELECT c_phone, c_acctbal FROM customer WHERE c_acctbal = 1000 ) AS subq_5 WHERE c_acctbal > 500 ORDER BY c_acctbal) AND l.l_tax >= 0.03372296939351626 AND l.l_linenumber >= 5 AND l.l_shipmode LIKE 'MAIL%' AND s.s_name LIKE 'Supplier#000008782%' AND s.s_acctbal > -622.4733642970616  LIMIT 30;

SELECT MIN(l.l_suppkey) AS min_l_l_suppkey, MAX(ps.ps_supplycost) AS max_ps_ps_supplycost, COUNT(l.l_quantity) AS count_l_l_quantity, SUM(l.l_discount) AS sum_l_l_discount, COUNT(l.l_shipDATE) AS count_l_l_shipDATE FROM lineitem l, nation n, partsupp ps WHERE EXISTS (SELECT DISTINCT p_brand FROM part UNION SELECT s_phone FROM supplier UNION SELECT s_phone FROM (SELECT DISTINCT s_phone FROM supplier AS s1_1 WHERE s_nationkey = 3) AS subq_1) AND n.n_name IN (SELECT n_name FROM nation WHERE n_nationkey IN (SELECT c_nationkey FROM customer WHERE c_acctbal > 1000 UNION SELECT s_nationkey FROM supplier WHERE s_acctbal < 500)) AND l.l_quantity = (SELECT COUNT(DISTINCT ps_suppkey) FROM partsupp WHERE ps_supplycost < 30 AND (ps_availqty = 50 OR ps_availqty = 150) AND ps_comment LIKE 'Regular%') AND EXISTS (SELECT n_name FROM (SELECT n_name FROM nation WHERE n_nationkey IN (SELECT c_nationkey FROM customer WHERE c_acctbal > 1000 ) UNION ALL SELECT n_name FROM nation WHERE n_regionkey = 1) t GROUP BY n_name ORDER BY n_name) AND ps.ps_suppkey > (SELECT COUNT(*) FROM (SELECT o_orderstatus FROM orders UNION ALL SELECT l_returnflag FROM lineitem ) t) AND ps.ps_partkey = l.l_partkey AND ps.ps_suppkey = l.l_suppkey AND l.l_suppkey = 5552 AND n.n_regionkey >= 0 AND l.l_partkey >= 49173 AND l.l_tax = 0.03845350295058449 AND l.l_quantity > 23.70147171608839  LIMIT 10;

SELECT COUNT(p.p_name) AS count_p_p_name, COUNT(r.r_regionkey) AS count_r_r_regionkey, AVG(l.l_orderkey) AS avg_l_l_orderkey, MIN(l.l_suppkey) AS min_l_l_suppkey, MIN(l.l_discount) AS min_l_l_discount FROM lineitem l, part p, region r WHERE r.r_name IN (SELECT r_name FROM region WHERE r_regionkey IN (SELECT n_regionkey FROM nation WHERE n_name LIKE 'A%' ) UNION SELECT r_name FROM region WHERE r_regionkey IN (SELECT n_regionkey FROM nation WHERE n_name NOT LIKE 'A%' ) ORDER BY r_name) AND EXISTS (SELECT c_name FROM (SELECT c_name FROM customer WHERE c_custkey IN (SELECT o_custkey FROM orders WHERE o_orderdate > '1995-01-01' UNION SELECT o_custkey FROM orders WHERE o_totalprice > 10000) UNION ALL SELECT c_name FROM customer WHERE c_custkey IN (SELECT o_custkey FROM orders WHERE o_orderpriority = '1-URGENT' UNION ALL SELECT o_custkey FROM orders WHERE o_orderstatus = 'F')) t GROUP BY c_name) AND p.p_brand IN (SELECT DISTINCT p_brand FROM part UNION SELECT DISTINCT s_address FROM supplier WHERE s_nationkey = 5 UNION SELECT DISTINCT l_comment FROM lineitem WHERE l_quantity > 25) AND r.r_regionkey = (SELECT COUNT(DISTINCT l_orderkey) FROM (SELECT l_orderkey, l_shipdate FROM lineitem WHERE l_quantity > 10 ) t) AND l.l_linenumber = (SELECT COUNT(DISTINCT c_custkey) FROM customer JOIN (SELECT o_custkey FROM orders WHERE o_totalprice < 500 UNION ALL SELECT o_custkey FROM orders WHERE o_orderdate < '1994-01-01') AS subq_5 ON customer.c_custkey = subq_5.o_custkey) AND l.l_partkey <= 178922 AND p.p_partkey >= 74528 AND p.p_brand LIKE 'Brand#11%' AND l.l_linestatus LIKE 'F%' AND p.p_name LIKE 'pink dodger cream orchid orange%'  LIMIT 30;

SELECT p.p_mfgr AS p_p_mfgr, MIN(p.p_retailprice) AS min_p_p_retailprice, p.p_size AS p_p_size, MIN(p.p_name) AS min_p_p_name, SUM(p.p_retailprice) AS sum_p_p_retailprice FROM part p WHERE EXISTS (SELECT o_clerk FROM (SELECT o_clerk, o_totalprice FROM orders ) AS subq_1 UNION SELECT p_name FROM part) AND p.p_partkey = (SELECT COUNT(*) FROM (SELECT c_phone FROM customer UNION ALL SELECT s_phone FROM supplier ) t) AND p.p_size IN (SELECT DISTINCT p_size FROM part UNION SELECT DISTINCT c_acctbal FROM customer WHERE c_mktsegment = 'AUTOMOBILE' UNION SELECT DISTINCT l_quantity FROM lineitem WHERE l_extendedprice < 100) AND EXISTS (SELECT COUNT(*) FROM (SELECT c_name FROM customer UNION SELECT s_name FROM (SELECT s_name, COUNT(*) FROM supplier GROUP BY s_name HAVING COUNT(*) > 2) AS subq_4) AS t_4) AND EXISTS (SELECT c_name FROM customer WHERE c_custkey IN (SELECT o_custkey FROM orders JOIN lineitem ON o_orderkey = l_orderkey WHERE l_discount > 0.05 UNION SELECT o_custkey FROM orders JOIN lineitem ON o_orderkey = l_orderkey WHERE l_discount < 0.10 UNION SELECT o_custkey FROM orders JOIN lineitem ON o_orderkey = l_orderkey WHERE l_discount > 0.15)) AND p.p_type LIKE 'SMALL BURNISHED TIN%' AND p.p_size > 48 AND p.p_partkey < 87511 AND p.p_name LIKE 'rosy mint honeydew turquoise seashell%' AND p.p_retailprice < 1749.313473471733  GROUP BY p.p_mfgr, p.p_size LIMIT 50;

SELECT MIN(l.l_receiptDATE) AS min_l_l_receiptDATE, MAX(l.l_extendedprice) AS max_l_l_extendedprice, MAX(l.l_quantity) AS max_l_l_quantity, MAX(l.l_linestatus) AS max_l_l_linestatus, SUM(l.l_quantity) AS sum_l_l_quantity FROM lineitem l WHERE l.l_extendedprice > (SELECT COUNT(*) FROM (SELECT r_name FROM region UNION ALL SELECT n_name FROM nation ) t) AND EXISTS (SELECT COUNT(l_quantity) FROM (SELECT l_quantity, l_returnflag FROM lineitem WHERE l_shipdate BETWEEN DATE '1996-01-01' AND DATE '1996-12-31' ) t GROUP BY l_returnflag ORDER BY l_returnflag) AND EXISTS (SELECT MAX(l_discount) FROM (SELECT l_discount, l_shipmode FROM lineitem WHERE l_commitdate BETWEEN DATE '1993-01-01' AND DATE '1993-12-31' ) t GROUP BY l_shipmode ORDER BY l_shipmode) AND l.l_extendedprice = (SELECT COUNT(DISTINCT r_regionkey) FROM region WHERE r_name = 'ASIA' AND (r_regionkey = 1 OR r_regionkey = 2) AND r_comment LIKE 'B%') AND EXISTS (SELECT DISTINCT p_name FROM part UNION SELECT s_comment FROM supplier UNION SELECT s_comment FROM (SELECT DISTINCT s_comment FROM supplier AS s1_5 WHERE s_acctbal > 3000) AS subq_5) AND l.l_orderkey < 4166636 AND l.l_quantity < 10.915939532752173 AND l.l_shipmode LIKE 'REG AIR%' AND l.l_suppkey >= 7384 AND l.l_tax = 0.050173150142609785  LIMIT 10;

SELECT MIN(c.c_custkey) AS min_c_c_custkey, MIN(c.c_name) AS min_c_c_name, MIN(l.l_commitDATE) AS min_l_l_commitDATE, MAX(p.p_retailprice) AS max_p_p_retailprice, COUNT(l.l_quantity) AS count_l_l_quantity FROM customer c, lineitem l, part p WHERE p.p_mfgr IN (SELECT DISTINCT p_mfgr FROM part UNION SELECT s_name FROM supplier UNION SELECT s_name FROM (SELECT DISTINCT s_name FROM supplier AS s1_1 WHERE s_acctbal < 5000) AS subq_1) AND c.c_address IN (SELECT c_address FROM (SELECT c_address, c_mktsegment FROM customer WHERE c_mktsegment = 'AUTOMOBILE' ) AS subq_2 WHERE c_mktsegment != 'BUILDING' ORDER BY c_mktsegment) AND l.l_partkey = (SELECT COUNT(DISTINCT p_partkey) FROM part JOIN (SELECT ps_partkey FROM partsupp WHERE ps_availqty > 75 UNION ALL SELECT ps_partkey FROM partsupp WHERE ps_supplycost < 15) AS subq_3 ON part.p_partkey = subq_3.ps_partkey) AND EXISTS (SELECT COUNT(p_size) FROM (SELECT p_size, p_type FROM part WHERE p_size < 15 ) t GROUP BY p_type ORDER BY p_type) AND p.p_name IN (SELECT p_name FROM part WHERE p_partkey IN (SELECT l_partkey FROM lineitem WHERE l_shipdate > '1995-06-30' UNION SELECT p_partkey FROM part WHERE p_retailprice < 150) AND p_size IN (SELECT p_size FROM part JOIN partsupp ON p_partkey = ps_partkey WHERE ps_availqty < 50)) AND l.l_discount = 0.09315328126268738 AND l.l_linestatus LIKE 'O%' AND c.c_custkey < 75069 AND p.p_name LIKE 'almond azure peach peru sky%' AND l.l_shipinstruct LIKE 'TAKE BACK RETURN%'  LIMIT 100;

SELECT c.c_custkey AS c_c_custkey, MAX(c.c_nationkey) AS max_c_c_nationkey, MAX(l.l_shipDATE) AS max_l_l_shipDATE, MAX(s.s_address) AS max_s_s_address, COUNT(l.l_commitDATE) AS count_l_l_commitDATE FROM customer c, lineitem l, orders o, region r, supplier s WHERE s.s_nationkey > (SELECT COUNT(DISTINCT ps_partkey) FROM partsupp WHERE ps_suppkey IN (SELECT s_suppkey FROM supplier WHERE s_acctbal > 7000 UNION SELECT s_suppkey FROM supplier WHERE s_nationkey = 2)) AND r.r_regionkey > (SELECT COUNT(DISTINCT s_suppkey) FROM supplier WHERE s_acctbal BETWEEN 1500 AND 2500 AND (s_nationkey = 5 OR s_nationkey = 6) AND s_phone LIKE '70%') AND c.c_comment IN (SELECT c_comment FROM (SELECT c_comment, c_nationkey FROM customer WHERE c_nationkey = 5 ) AS subq_3 WHERE c_nationkey > 4 ORDER BY c_nationkey) AND l.l_extendedprice > (SELECT COUNT(DISTINCT p_partkey) FROM (SELECT p_partkey FROM part WHERE p_size > 10 UNION ALL SELECT ps_partkey FROM partsupp WHERE ps_supplycost < 50) t JOIN supplier ON s_suppkey = t.p_partkey) AND o.o_orderstatus IN (SELECT o_orderstatus FROM (SELECT o_orderstatus, o_orderdate FROM orders ) AS subq_5 UNION SELECT n_comment FROM nation) AND o.o_custkey = c.c_custkey AND o.o_orderkey = l.l_orderkey AND l.l_returnflag LIKE 'N%' AND l.l_shipinstruct LIKE 'DELIVER IN PERSON%' AND l.l_commitdate < '1992-02-12' AND l.l_suppkey < 4165 AND o.o_orderpriority LIKE '5-LOW%'  GROUP BY c.c_custkey LIMIT 50;

SELECT COUNT(p.p_retailprice) AS count_p_p_retailprice, MIN(p.p_partkey) AS min_p_p_partkey, COUNT(p.p_mfgr) AS count_p_p_mfgr, MAX(p.p_size) AS max_p_p_size, COUNT(p.p_name) AS count_p_p_name FROM part p WHERE EXISTS (SELECT AVG(l_quantity) FROM (SELECT l_quantity, l_linestatus FROM lineitem JOIN part ON l_partkey = p_partkey ) AS t_1 GROUP BY l_linestatus ORDER BY l_linestatus) AND EXISTS (SELECT DISTINCT l_returnflag FROM (SELECT l_returnflag FROM lineitem UNION ALL SELECT o_orderstatus FROM orders) AS u_2 JOIN customer ON u_2.l_returnflag = c_phone) AND p.p_partkey = (SELECT COUNT(DISTINCT c_custkey) FROM customer JOIN (SELECT o_custkey FROM orders WHERE o_totalprice > 1000 UNION ALL SELECT o_custkey FROM orders WHERE o_orderdate > '1995-01-01') AS subq_3 ON customer.c_custkey = subq_3.o_custkey) AND EXISTS (SELECT DISTINCT c_name FROM customer UNION SELECT n_name FROM nation UNION SELECT n_name FROM (SELECT DISTINCT n_name FROM nation AS n1_4 WHERE n_regionkey = 1) AS subq_4) AND p.p_size > (SELECT COUNT(DISTINCT s_suppkey) FROM supplier WHERE s_acctbal > 800 AND (s_nationkey = 4 OR s_nationkey = 8) AND 3+5=8 AND s_nationkey IN (SELECT n_nationkey FROM nation WHERE n_regionkey = 2 AND 4*6=24)) AND p.p_name LIKE 'metallic burnished gainsboro almond dim%' AND p.p_brand LIKE 'Brand#35%' AND p.p_mfgr LIKE 'Manufacturer#4%' AND p.p_retailprice >= 1100.583961066872 AND p.p_size = 27  LIMIT 50;

SELECT MIN(c.c_comment) AS min_c_c_comment, SUM(c.c_nationkey) AS sum_c_c_nationkey, MAX(c.c_comment) AS max_c_c_comment, MIN(c.c_nationkey) AS min_c_c_nationkey, c.c_comment AS c_c_comment FROM customer c WHERE EXISTS (SELECT n_comment FROM nation WHERE n_nationkey IN (SELECT s_nationkey FROM supplier WHERE s_acctbal > 2000 ) UNION SELECT n_comment FROM nation WHERE n_nationkey IN (SELECT s_nationkey FROM supplier WHERE s_acctbal < 2000 ) ORDER BY n_comment) AND EXISTS (SELECT AVG(s_acctbal) FROM (SELECT s_acctbal, s_name FROM supplier JOIN region ON s_nationkey = r_regionkey WHERE r_name = 'ASIA' UNION SELECT s_acctbal, s_name FROM supplier JOIN partsupp ON s_suppkey = ps_suppkey WHERE ps_supplycost < 100 AND ps_availqty IN (SELECT ps_availqty FROM partsupp WHERE ps_partkey > 1000)) AS subq_2 GROUP BY s_name) AND c.c_custkey IN (SELECT DISTINCT c_custkey FROM customer UNION SELECT o_custkey FROM orders WHERE o_totalprice > 1000) AND EXISTS (SELECT p_name FROM (SELECT p_name FROM part WHERE p_partkey IN (SELECT l_partkey FROM lineitem WHERE l_shipdate < '1995-01-01' ) UNION ALL SELECT p_name FROM part WHERE p_retailprice > 100) t GROUP BY p_name ORDER BY p_name) AND EXISTS (SELECT l_returnflag FROM (SELECT l_returnflag FROM lineitem WHERE l_orderkey IN (SELECT o_orderkey FROM orders WHERE o_orderdate > '1996-12-31' ) UNION ALL SELECT l_returnflag FROM lineitem WHERE l_discount > 0.05) t GROUP BY l_returnflag ORDER BY l_returnflag) AND c.c_custkey <= 38310 AND c.c_acctbal = 9732.02138883703 AND c.c_name LIKE 'Customer#000022846%' AND c.c_mktsegment LIKE 'FURNITURE%' AND c.c_nationkey >= 0  GROUP BY c.c_comment LIMIT 100;

SELECT COUNT(s.s_comment) AS count_s_s_comment, MIN(o.o_shippriority) AS min_o_o_shippriority, SUM(o.o_totalprice) AS sum_o_o_totalprice, MAX(o.o_custkey) AS max_o_o_custkey, MIN(s.s_name) AS min_s_s_name FROM orders o, supplier s WHERE EXISTS (SELECT o_totalprice FROM (SELECT o_totalprice, o_custkey FROM orders WHERE o_custkey = 10 ) AS subq_1 WHERE o_custkey > 9 ORDER BY o_custkey) AND s.s_acctbal IN (SELECT s_acctbal FROM (SELECT s_acctbal, s_nationkey FROM supplier WHERE s_nationkey = 5 ) AS subq_2 WHERE s_nationkey > 4 ORDER BY s_nationkey) AND EXISTS (SELECT DISTINCT o_clerk FROM (SELECT o_clerk FROM orders UNION ALL SELECT c_phone FROM customer) AS u_3 JOIN lineitem ON u_3.o_clerk = l_shipinstruct) AND o.o_totalprice > (SELECT COUNT(DISTINCT p_partkey) FROM part JOIN (SELECT ps_partkey FROM partsupp WHERE ps_availqty > 100 UNION ALL SELECT ps_partkey FROM partsupp WHERE ps_supplycost > 20) AS subq_4 ON part.p_partkey = subq_4.ps_partkey) AND EXISTS (SELECT n_name FROM (SELECT n_name, n_regionkey FROM nation ) AS subq_5 UNION SELECT p_container FROM part) AND s.s_acctbal > 4354.58499180421 AND s.s_suppkey < 6110 AND s.s_nationkey >= 4 AND s.s_name LIKE 'Supplier#000000382%' AND o.o_orderpriority LIKE '1-URGENT%'  LIMIT 10;

SELECT MIN(s.s_phone) AS min_s_s_phone, AVG(p.p_retailprice) AS avg_p_p_retailprice, p.p_type AS p_p_type, MIN(p.p_brand) AS min_p_p_brand, p.p_comment AS p_p_comment FROM part p, supplier s WHERE EXISTS (SELECT r_comment FROM region WHERE r_regionkey IN (SELECT n_regionkey FROM nation WHERE n_name LIKE 'E%' ) UNION SELECT r_comment FROM region WHERE r_regionkey IN (SELECT n_regionkey FROM nation WHERE n_name NOT LIKE 'E%' ) ORDER BY r_comment) AND p.p_type IN (SELECT p_type FROM (SELECT p_type, p_size FROM part ) AS subq_2 UNION SELECT s_name FROM supplier) AND s.s_name IN (SELECT DISTINCT s_name FROM supplier UNION SELECT p_name FROM part UNION SELECT p_name FROM (SELECT DISTINCT p_name FROM part AS p1_3 WHERE p_size > 10) AS subq_3) AND EXISTS (SELECT r_comment FROM (SELECT r_comment, r_regionkey FROM region ) AS subq_4 UNION SELECT l_comment FROM lineitem) AND EXISTS (SELECT p_name FROM part WHERE p_partkey IN (SELECT l_partkey FROM lineitem WHERE l_shipdate > '1996-01-01' ) UNION SELECT p_name FROM part WHERE p_partkey IN (SELECT l_partkey FROM lineitem WHERE l_shipdate < '1996-01-01' ) ORDER BY p_name) AND p.p_retailprice >= 1878.6858510937604 AND p.p_partkey = 141228 AND s.s_name LIKE 'Supplier#000001066%' AND p.p_type LIKE 'PROMO PLATED NICKEL%' AND p.p_mfgr LIKE 'Manufacturer#2%'  GROUP BY p.p_type, p.p_comment LIMIT 100;

SELECT o.o_orderDATE AS o_o_orderDATE, SUM(o.o_orderkey) AS sum_o_o_orderkey, COUNT(o.o_orderkey) AS count_o_o_orderkey, MAX(o.o_shippriority) AS max_o_o_shippriority, MAX(o.o_orderDATE) AS max_o_o_orderDATE FROM nation n, orders o WHERE EXISTS (SELECT s_acctbal FROM supplier WHERE s_suppkey IN (SELECT ps_suppkey FROM partsupp WHERE ps_availqty > 60 ) UNION SELECT s_acctbal FROM supplier WHERE s_suppkey IN (SELECT ps_suppkey FROM partsupp WHERE ps_availqty < 60 ) ORDER BY s_acctbal) AND n.n_name IN (SELECT n_name FROM nation WHERE n_nationkey IN (SELECT c_nationkey FROM customer WHERE c_acctbal > 5000 ) UNION SELECT n_name FROM nation WHERE n_nationkey IN (SELECT c_nationkey FROM customer WHERE c_acctbal < 5000 ) ORDER BY n_name) AND EXISTS (SELECT COUNT(c_custkey) FROM (SELECT c_custkey, c_mktsegment FROM customer WHERE c_acctbal > 1000 ) t GROUP BY c_mktsegment ORDER BY c_mktsegment) AND o.o_totalprice > (SELECT COUNT(DISTINCT l_suppkey) FROM (SELECT l_suppkey FROM lineitem WHERE l_discount > 0.05 UNION ALL SELECT ps_suppkey FROM partsupp WHERE ps_supplycost > 60) t JOIN part ON p_partkey = t.l_suppkey) AND EXISTS (SELECT DISTINCT n_name FROM nation UNION SELECT c_name FROM customer UNION SELECT c_name FROM (SELECT DISTINCT c_name FROM customer AS c1_5 WHERE c_acctbal < 2000) AS subq_5) AND o.o_orderpriority LIKE '3-MEDIUM%' AND o.o_totalprice > 57586.13320795836 AND n.n_regionkey < 3 AND o.o_orderstatus LIKE 'O%' AND o.o_orderdate >= '1998-06-23'  GROUP BY o.o_orderDATE LIMIT 100;

SELECT SUM(l.l_partkey) AS sum_l_l_partkey, l.l_linestatus AS l_l_linestatus, n.n_comment AS n_n_comment, l.l_shipinstruct AS l_l_shipinstruct, MAX(l.l_discount) AS max_l_l_discount FROM lineitem l, nation n WHERE n.n_regionkey > (SELECT COUNT(DISTINCT s_suppkey) FROM (SELECT s_suppkey, s_phone FROM supplier WHERE s_acctbal < 3000 ) t) AND EXISTS (SELECT p_2.p_type FROM part p_2 WHERE p_2.p_partkey IN (SELECT l_2.l_partkey FROM lineitem l_2 WHERE l_2.l_quantity > 30 UNION ALL SELECT l2_2.l_partkey FROM lineitem l2_2 WHERE l2_2.l_extendedprice < 500 GROUP BY l2_2.l_partkey) AND p_2.p_size > 10) AND EXISTS (SELECT p_3.p_container FROM part p_3 WHERE p_3.p_partkey IN (SELECT l_3.l_partkey FROM lineitem l_3 WHERE l_3.l_quantity < 20 UNION ALL SELECT l2_3.l_partkey FROM lineitem l2_3 WHERE l2_3.l_extendedprice > 1000 GROUP BY l2_3.l_partkey) AND p_3.p_size < 5) AND l.l_tax > (SELECT COUNT(*) FROM (SELECT c_phone FROM customer UNION ALL SELECT s_phone FROM supplier ) t) AND EXISTS (SELECT l_shipmode FROM (SELECT l_shipmode FROM lineitem WHERE l_orderkey IN (SELECT o_orderkey FROM orders WHERE o_orderdate < '1994-01-01' ) UNION ALL SELECT l_shipmode FROM lineitem WHERE l_quantity > 25) t GROUP BY l_shipmode ORDER BY l_shipmode) AND l.l_shipdate <= '1994-05-31' AND l.l_linestatus LIKE 'O%' AND l.l_receiptdate >= '1993-05-14' AND l.l_quantity = 13.952365764474443 AND l.l_orderkey < 2894436  GROUP BY n.n_comment, l.l_linestatus, l.l_shipinstruct LIMIT 30;
